As the chosen guys get ready to leave, The Vile Force arrives, two bots 
standing in front of Trainwreck,  and one on each side. Vile then steps 
forward from the front and laughs evily as all his men ready to open fire.

Vile: "Oh... Im so sorry but you can't leave yet... your still needed here. 
Let me and my men help you Realize that."

Vile laughs again before his chest opens up and two large blasts of 
antimatter are sent at train wreck from his dual chest imbedded Antimatter 
bazooka. He then follows that up by a powerful blast from his tackion cannon, 
time and space being warped around the blast. THe person Next to him, Methos 
then Flys straight up into the air and activates his double bladed energy 
scythe and then attempts to slash into Trainwreck from the beggining to the 
end. On the Right side of Trainwreck Gemini 1 laughs as he opens fire on him 
with his double fusion cannon once and with 2 missiles from his shoulder 
mounted double missiles launcher. And on the left side Gemini 2 simply smirks 
as he opens fire on Trainwreck with his ionic fusion cannon and three 
missiles from the triple missile launcher on his shoulder.

--part1_26.18264163.288195af_boundary
